node.text:
Winner is: @elaine.gravey 

NORWAY GIVEAWAY!😍👇🏻
We are giving you a chance to win a free stay at the magical resort @auroraborealisobservatory 
and @aarorbuer_lofoten in Senja/Lofoten, North Norway. 

Winner will also get a free dinner at 
@eggenrestaurant and entry to the brand new @romsdalsgondolen - a new way to experience the fantastic views of the mountains and fjords in Romsdalen, Norway🇳🇴

To enter: 
1. Follow @romsdalen.no , @aarorbuer_lofoten &  @romsdalsgondolen 
2. Like this post
3. Tag a friend (1 tag = 1 entry, enter as many times as you wish).
4. (Bonus) Share this post on your IG Story for an additional entry!

The winner will be chosen randomly on 20. august 2021. Open internationally.
Good luck!! 💙
—
(This giveaway is not sponsored by Instagram)
